{"tid":1503033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你肯做多少少，前線就會安全好多","createTime":"2019-08-24T19:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T04:28:57.000Z","uid":198258,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b12b8bff27a0dc535310c90eff5d5f8763b87ad","tid":1503033,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:58:18.000Z","msg":"打唔落手就帶下蛋，口講升級左咁耐問下自己除左計人頭仲可唔可以做多少少？<br />\n<br />\n我知每個人心到都有條線，可能係驚告重罪，可能係太聖人，此終唔肯出手。<br />\n<br />\n蛋打唔死人，蛋唔係攻擊性武器。<br />\n<br />\n但如果好彩打中左，分分鐘就係呢一下而救左一個手足。<br />\n<br />\n講好左齊上齊落，有班兄弟信左你去幫你打狗，諗緊點樣保護你。你又諗緊啲咩？諗緊點樣就算比人拉都告唔入重罪？<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係冇當前線係condom,可唔可以分擔番少少嘅風險？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非唔該唔好淨係把口升級，每一個聽日都同我帶雞蛋先好行出黎</span></span>"},{"pid":"4557e0a112179da80fbb7d5ea2c979d8fc23e45e","tid":1503033,"uid":198258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:59:36.000Z","msg":"拒做freerider"},{"pid":"b7f2398c9a2118208edc880faf9726803e6fcd46","tid":1503033,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:00:49.000Z","msg":"和理升級》雞蛋兵"},{"pid":"d060a91f71f2abce1e5553796f078f50192b6505","tid":1503033,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:01:00.000Z","msg":"和理升級》雞蛋兵"},{"pid":"88014b427c5aea3168f623d597906235c3392114","tid":1503033,"uid":312492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:01:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1502375/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1502375/page/1</a><br />\n整ABS板盾牌分享<br />\n借位推俾啲唔夠Gear嘅手足睇"},{"pid":"8caa9e189106aa7917c11950955c08a9c8152a1d","tid":1503033,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:01:11.000Z","msg":"和理升級》雞蛋兵"},{"pid":"8d3e0281754c8bdfdac4ebbc87a0890234653512","tid":1503033,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:01:25.000Z","msg":"和理升級》雞蛋兵"},{"pid